title: Path of Exile Bot Exiled-Bot v0.70f
description:
Exiled-bot: The Famous Path of Exile Bot

Features:
    Fully passive (no injection - low risk)!!
    Monster searching and killing
    Pathfinding and area exploring
    Endgame Maps farming and crafting
    The bot takes flasks and chicken
    Gems leveling
    Auras handling
    Picks up orbs, gems, scrolls, and maps!
    Fully configurable PickIt!
    Vendoring
    Inventory stasher
    User can configure the items he wants the bot to pickup (rares, 6S, 5L, ...)
    Highly configurable
    Automatic game restart and zone cleaning
    Combat routines customization
    Main quests and progression for Act 1 and Act 2 (for now)

Currently working with game version 2.6.2 and should work with similar versions as well.

Usage guide and more info at https://exiled-bot.net/
